---
<section class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621905251189-08b45d6a269e?q=80&w=2069&auto=format&fit=crop" 
            alt="Técnico profesional reparando aire acondicionado minisplit"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
        <!-- Overlay -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/90 via-blue-900/70 to-blue-800/40"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 py-12">
        <div class="max-w-3xl animate-hero">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 backdrop-blur-md border border-blue-400/30 text-blue-200 text-xs md:text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
                <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                    <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-75"></span>
                    <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-blue-500"></span>
                </span>
                Servicio Técnico en Reynosa
            </span>
            
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight md:leading-tight lg:leading-tight mb-6">
                ¿Calor en Reynosa? <br/>
                <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-300 to-cyan-200">
                    Soluciones Inmediatas.
                </span>
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-200 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
                Especialistas en **Minisplits y Lavadoras**. Servicio honesto, refacciones nuevas y garantía por escrito para su total tranquilidad.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                <a href="#" class="px-8 py-4 bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-icons-outlined">whatsapp</span>
                    Cotizar por WhatsApp
                </a>
                <a href="#servicios" class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-900 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                    Ver Nuestros Servicios
                    <span class="material-icons-outlined text-sm transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">arrow_forward</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Decorative bottom wave or blur -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-white dark:from-gray-900 to-transparent z-10"></div>
</section>

<style>
    .animate-hero {
        animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
</style>
